[30;1m150 | [0m[35m<span id="s-umfpack"></span><h2>General Linear Equations<a class="headerlink" href="#general-linear-[0m
[30;1m151 | [0m[35m<p>The module <code class="xref py py-mod docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">cvxopt.umf[0m

[30;1m1616 | [0m[35m        In some cases, the returned solution may be fairly accurate.  If[0m

[30;1m1618 | [0m[35m        are small, then x, y, s, z are close to optimal.[0m
